## 1. MISSION CRITICAL: THE "VALLEY-FIRST" MANDATE
FarmSense is a **Sovereign-Grade Water Infrastructure** company based in **Monte Vista, Colorado**. 

Our mission is to ensure that water data—the most valuable resource of the 21st century—stays under the control of the local community. We are building the "Operating System for Global Water," based in **Monte Vista**, with our first validation pilot starting at CSU SLV RC in **Center, Colorado**.

